rman are essentially the same duties the boards chairman normally undertakes.";i:34;s:73:"Think of the vice-chair as the future leader of your organizations board.";i:35;s:44:"The vice-chair tackles the following duties.";i:36;s:49:"Prepares to assume the office of the board chair.";i:37;s:96:"Fulfills the board chairs duties when the presiding officer is absent or if that office becomes.";i:38;s:52:"What do we and the club expect from a vice chairman.";i:39;s:121:"To support the chair in the provision of direction and leadership to the club dealing with issues as and when they arise.";i:40;s:86:"To assist the chairperson in the planning and delivery of club and committee meetings.";i:41;s:185:"Responsibilities other than those detailed in the governing document establishing clear roles and responsibilities for the Chairperson can improve the performance of the governing body.";i:42;s:71:"The roles and responsibilities of a Chair should include the following.";}}